  EffectDiscription_ENG: "DigiXros -2: [OmniShoutmon] \xD7 [ZeigGreymon] \xD7 [Ballistamon]
    \xD7 [Dorulumon] \xD7 [Starmons] \xD7 [Sparrowmon]\uFF1CRush\uFF1E (This Digimon
    may attack the turn it was played.)\uFF1CMaterial Save 4\uFF1E (When this Digimon
    is deleted, you may place 4 cards in this Digimon's DigiXros conditions from
